<h2>What are the guidelines</h2>(may change in the future)
<ul>
  <li>Language is english only</li>
  <li>
    Quality over quantity. Don't mass create topics; but create a few meaningfull ones. Try to avoid empty topics.
    Try to identify and point to similar/duplicated topics when possible
  </li>
  <li>No OC on the site, just links to content on other sites</li>
  <li>First person to submit vote gets upvotes. Reposts of a link already submitted should be downvoted or flagged.</li>
</ul>

